00:00:14.696 --> 00:00:20.524
this square root is simply what's inside here. On the right side, we'll square

00:00:20.524 --> 00:00:26.040
the binomial x plus 2 to get this expression. Next we'll distribute the 4 to

00:00:26.040 --> 00:00:32.073
get 8x plus 16 on the left, and our same expression on the right. We want to

00:00:32.073 --> 00:00:36.178
set our quadratic equal to 0, so we subtract 8x from both sides, and we

00:00:36.178 --> 00:00:43.002
subtract 16 from both sides. This leaves us with 0 equals x squared minus 4x

00:00:43.002 --> 00:00:48.535
